# KOS Concepts
<kos/application/type/infrastructure> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type> ; rdfs:label "Infrastructure Application"@en .
<kos/application/type/business> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type> ; rdfs:label "Business Application"@en .
<kos/application/business-importance/high> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/business-importance> ; rdfs:label "High Business Importance"@en .
<kos/application/business-importance/medium> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/business-importance> ; rdfs:label "Medium Business Importance"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/status/InProduction> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/status> ; rdfs:label "In Production"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/status/Development> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/status> ; rdfs:label "Development"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/sla-level/Gold> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/sla-level> ; rdfs:label "Gold SLA Level"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/sla-level/Silver> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/sla-level> ; rdfs:label "Silver SLA Level"@en .

<kos/TroubleTicket/severity/Critical> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/severity> ; rdfs:label "Critical Severity"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/severity/Major> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/severity> ; rdfs:label "Major Severity"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/type/Failure> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/type> ; rdfs:label "Failure Type"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/type/Assistance> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/type> ; rdfs:label "Assistance Type"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/category/TotalBreakdown> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/category> ; rdfs:label "Total Breakdown Category"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/category/IsolatedCustomerSite> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/category> ; rdfs:label "Isolated Customer Site Category"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/priority/P1> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/priority> ; rdfs:label "Priority 1"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/priority/P2> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/priority> ; rdfs:label "Priority 2"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/origin/Supervision> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/origin> ; rdfs:label "Supervision Origin"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/origin/Customer> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/origin> ; rdfs:label "Customer Origin"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/urgency/ImmediateIntervention> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/urgency> ; rdfs:label "Immediate Intervention Urgency"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/problemResponsibility/ManagedBackboneNetworks> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/problemResponsibility> ; rdfs:label "Managed Backbone Networks Responsibility"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/commentType/Internal> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/commentType> ; rdfs:label "Internal Comment Type"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/operationType/Diagnosis> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/operationType> ; rdfs:label "Diagnosis Operation Type"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/status/InProgress> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/status> ; rdfs:label "In Progress Status"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/status/Resolved> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/status> ; rdfs:label "Resolved Status"@en .
<kos/TroubleTicket/status/Closed> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/status> ; rdfs:label "Closed Status"@en .


<kos/ChangeRequest/category/InternalIntervention> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/ChangeRequest/category> ; rdfs:label "Internal Intervention Category"@en .
